title: 'X-Files' Revival Episode Debuts During New York Comic-Con!
text: David Duchovny visits the SiriusXM Studios at The X-Files panel during 2015 New York Comic-Con held at The Jacob K. Javits Convention Center on Saturday (October 10) in New York City.
